    "Although the intelligence community in Germany works in English due to international structures such as NATO, the United Nations and the EU, its own products are created in German.",
    "Accordingly, deepCOM's user interface and output are in German.",
    "Standard searches in text databases are based on the frequency of occurrence of words.",
    "Accordingly, texts that contain more of the search terms will appear higher up on the list.",
    "In this method, also known as Bag of Words (BOW), the sheer frequency of the individual words determines a good search hit, not their relationship to one another (Qader et al., 2019)."
  ],
